\c 6
\s Umlayo omkhulu
\p
\v 1 Lale yimilayo, izimiso, lezahlulelo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu elaya ukulifundisa, ukuthi lizenze elizweni elichaphela kulo ukuthi lidle ilifa lalo\x + 4.1. 5.31. 12.1.\x*,
\v 2 ukuze uyesabe iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina zonke izimiso zayo lemithetho yayo engikulaya yona, wena lendodana yakho lendodana yendodana yakho, zonke izinsuku zempilo yakho\x + 6.13,24. 10.12,13,20. 13.4. Hlab. 111.10. 128.1. Tshu. 12.13.\x*, ukuze insuku zakho zelulwe\x + 4.40. Zaga 3.1,2.\x*.
\v 3 Ngakho zwana, Israyeli, unanzelele ukuzenza, ukuze kukulungele, ukuze wande kakhulu\x + 4.40. Zaga 3.1,2.\x*, njengokuthembisa kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyihlo kuwe\x + Gen. 15.5. 22.17.\x*, elizweni eligeleza uchago loluju\x + Eks. 3.8.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Zwana, Israyeli, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, yiN\nd kosi\nd* yinye\x + Mark. 12.29; Isa. 42.8. Joha. 17.3. 1 Kor. 8.4,6.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo wothanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke\x + 10.12. 11.1,13. 30.6. Mat. 22.37. Mark. 12.30. Luka 10.27.\x* langomphefumulo wakho wonke langamandla akho wonke.\x + 2 Kho. 23.25.\x*
\v 6 Njalo amazwi la engikulaya ngawo lamuhla azakuba senhliziyweni yakho\x + 11.18. 32.46. Hlab. 37.31. 119.11. Isa. 51.7. Hez. 40.4.\x*;
\v 7 njalo uzawafundisa abantwana bakho ngokukhuthala, uzakhuluma ngawo lapho uhlezi endlini yakho, lalapho uhamba endleleni, lalapho ulala, lalapho uvuka\x + 4.9.\x*.
\v 8 Uzawabophela esandleni sakho abe luphawu, njalo abe \w ngamafilakteriyu\w** phakathi laphakathi kwamehlo akho\x + Eks. 13.9. Zaga 3.3. 6.21. 7.3.\x*.
\v 9 Njalo uzawabhala emigubazini yendlu yakho, lemasangweni akho\x + 11.20. Isa. 57.8.\x*.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli baxwayiswa ngokungalaleli
\p
\v 10 Kuzakuthi lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikungenisa elizweni eyafunga kuboyihlo, kuAbrahama, kuIsaka lakuJakobe, ukukunika imizi emikhulu lemihle, ongayakhanga\x + Josh. 11.13. 24.13. Hlab. 105.44.\x*,
\v 11 lezindlu ezigcwele zonke izinto ezinhle, ongazigcwalisanga, lemithombo eyagejwayo ongayigebhanga, izivini lezihlahla zemihlwathi ongazihlanyelanga, lapho udlile wasutha\x + 8.9,10.\x*,
\v 12 ziqaphele, hlezi uyikhohlwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakukhupha elizweni leGibhithe, endlini yobugqili.
\v 13 Uzayesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, uyikhonze\x + 6.2. Mat. 4.10. Luka 4.8.\x*, ufunge ngebizo layo\x + Hlab. 63.11. Isa. 45.23. 65.16. Jer. 12.16. Zef. 1.5.\x*.
\v 14 Lingalandeli abanye onkulunkulu\x + 8.19. 11.28. Jer. 25.6.\x*, babonkulunkulu bezizwe ezilizungelezeleyo\x + 13.7.\x*.
\v 15 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho inguNkulunkulu olobukhwele phakathi kwakho\x + Eks. 20.5.\x*, hlezi ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho lukuvuthele, ikuchithe usuke ebusweni bomhlaba\x + 7.4. 11.17.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Lingayilingi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Mat. 4.7. Luka 4.12.\x* njengalokhu layilinga eMasa\x + Eks. 17.2,7. 1 Kor. 10. 9.\x*.
\v 17 Ligcine lokugcina imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, lobufakazi bayo, lezimiso zayo, ekulaye zona\x + 11.22. Hlab. 119.4.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo wenze okuqondileyo lokulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuze kukulungele, lokuthi ungene udle ilifa lelizwe elihle, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyalifungela oyihlo\x + 4.40.\x*,
\v 19 ukuxotsha zonke izitha zakho phambi kwakho, njengalokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile\x + Nani 33.52,53.\x*.
\v 20 Lapho indodana yakho ikubuza esikhathini esizayo isithi: Buyini ubufakazi lezimiso lezahlulelo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu elilaye zona\x + Eks. 13.14.\x*?
\v 21 Khona uzakuthi endodaneni yakho: Sasiyizigqili zikaFaro eGibhithe, leN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhupha eGibhithe ngesandla esilamandla\x + 4.34.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza izibonakaliso lezimangaliso ezinkulu lezimbi eGibhithe, phezu kukaFaro laphezu kwendlu yakhe yonke, phambi kwamehlo ethu\x + Hlab. 135.9. Dute. 4.34.\x*.
\v 23 Yasikhupha khona ukuze isingenise, ukusinika ilizwe eyalifungela obaba.
\v 24 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisilaya ukwenza zonke lezizimiso, ukwesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 6.2,13.\x*, ukuze kusilungele insuku zonke\x + 10.13. Jer. 32.39.\x*, ukusilondoloza siphila njengalamuhla\x + Hlab. 41.2. 4.1. 8.1. Levi 18.5.\x*.
\v 25 Kuzakuba yikulunga kithi, uba sinanzelela ukwenza limilayo yonke phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wethu, njengokusilaya kwayo\x + 24.13.\x*.
